data.description: Don't miss this 2022-built waterfront property! Upgrades galore! This 1680 SF home was built for an employee and is not your typical model. Features include Level 6 granite, LVP flooring throughout (no carpet), tile backsplash, RO System, 36" cabinets, Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, crown molding, pantry, soft close cabinet doors, electrical outlets in the floor of the family room, termite prevention system, bubble jet tub, custom shower tile, epoxy garage floor, cul-de-sac lot, seawall, stone front, landscape sprinkler system, ADT security system, and R-38 insulation in the attic. Call for your tour of this customized home and make it yours!
